snippet: The U.S. Navy said on Wednesday that 151 sailors had been disqualified from working as sexual assault counselors and other positions as the military tries to improve how it helps victims following a string of high-profile sexual assault cases....

headline.print_headline: U.S. Navy Bars 151 Sailors From Jobs After Sex Assault Review
headline.main: U.S. Navy Bars 151 Sailors From Jobs After Sex Assault Review

lead_paragraph: The U.S. Navy said on Wednesday that 151 sailors had been disqualified from working as sexual assault counselors and other positions as the military tries to improve how it helps victims following a string of high-profile sexual assault cases.
